com.misc.common.moplaf.time.discrete

Interface MergeElement

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MergeElementImpl

    public interface MergeElement
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Merge Element'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Bucket From
    • Bucket To
    • Previous
    • Next
    • Part From In To
    • Part To In From
    • Element Start
    • Element End
    • Seconds
    See Also:
    DiscretePackage.getMergeElement()
